{"tid":590824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國客不甘買限量品被拒　在日當街毆打保安員","createTime":"2018-03-13T03:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T03:24:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":178,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"4903a646cff796c0e9940a4ab29d9d28fe1dc3af","tid":590824,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T03:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180313/s00005/218ded170dfb2d52e5a5c1175c53a25d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180313%2Fs00005%2F218ded170dfb2d52e5a5c1175c53a25d.jpg&h=c2358d02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本澀谷街頭發生毆鬥事件，一群內地客在日本排隊購物時，被店員認出常走水貨，故拒絕售賣商品。雙方理論期間發生衝突，內地客惱羞成怒，用椅子毆打對方。<br />\n<br />\n事發上周五（9日），潮牌「Supreme」一間位於日本澀谷的分店推出限量商品，引來大批人群排隊搶購。但由於該品牌嚴禁客人轉售限量商品，10多名前往水貨的內地人，排隊期間已被工作人員認出，於是拒絕販賣。<br />\n<br />\n這群內地人被拒後上前理論，但依然被拒，於是和在場保安員發生衝突。圍觀群眾拍下影片放上網後被瘋傳，影片中可見，一群黑衣男子用摺凳和雨傘作武器，砸向一名保安員，其間雙方互相推撞，用日語互罵，還有人用普通話說髒話，後來有再一名保安出現調解。事件令部分日本網民表示，對中國人更反感。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180313/s00005/1520904640156\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180313%2Fs00005%2F1520904640156&d=M2J4%2BtcXLJ4gd8wtiZWwY5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=d8c630db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180313%2Fs00005%2F1520904640156&h=2e8832d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180313/s00005/1520904640156</a>"},{"pid":"932bbbf23cd3bff46bb85ffdd2c64773860b7ba3","tid":590824,"uid":52215,"like":14,"dislike":93,"score":-79,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T03:43:52.000Z","msg":"算吧啦<br />\n呢D 垃圾牌子唔駛做呢D新聞出黎谷人氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cbab77fc2c3d3c4021f3a7cf4cb6c6d7187458","tid":590824,"uid":64060,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"quote":{"pid":"4903a646cff796c0e9940a4a